# Airflow SPCS Deployment Configuration
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values:
#   cp .env.example .env
#
# Note: Snowflake connection credentials are NOT needed here.
# DAGs use SPCS native OAuth tokens automatically — zero-config.
# See dags/snowflake_etl_pipeline.py for the pattern.
#
# This file is reserved for future local overrides (e.g., custom warehouse names).
# The .env file is gitignored and never committed.
